text: Park Je-un (born 11 March 1993) is a South Korean Nordic combined skier who competes internationally.FIS profile He competed at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of South Korea Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:South Korean male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of South Korea Category:Ski jumpers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
